洛伦兹系统是一个常微分方程组，系统参数的默认值为 \((\sigma = 10, \rho = 28, \beta = 8/3)\)，初值为 \((-13, -14, 47)\)。\[\begin{equation*}
\left\{ 
  \begin{array}{l}
    \frac{\partial x}{\partial t} = \sigma (y - x) \\
    \frac{\partial y}{\partial t} = x(\rho -z) - y \\
    \frac{\partial x}{\partial t} = xy - \beta z
  \end{array} \right.
\end{equation*}\]调用 scatterplot3d 绘制三维曲线图，如图34.15 所示
