ReacTran 的几个关键函数介绍一维热传导方程\[\begin{equation*}
\left\{ 
  \begin{array}{l}
    \frac{\partial y}{\partial t} = D \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial x^2}
  \end{array} \right.
\end{equation*}\]参数 \(D = 0.01\)，边界条件 \(y_{t,x=0} = 0, y_{t, x = 1} = 1\)，初始条件 \(y_{t=0,x} = \sin(\pi x)\)。
