二维拉普拉斯方程\[\begin{equation*}
\left\{ 
  \begin{array}{l}
    \frac{\partial^2 u}{\partial^2 x} + \frac{\partial^2 u}{\partial y^2} = 0
  \end{array} \right.
\end{equation*}\]边界条件\[\begin{equation*}
\left\{ 
  \begin{array}{l}
    u_{x=0,y} = u_{x=1,y} = 0 \\
    \frac{\partial u_{x, y=0}}{\partial y} = 0 \\
    \frac{\partial u_{x,y=1}}{\partial y} = \pi\sinh(\pi)\sin(\pi x)
  \end{array} \right.
\end{equation*}\]它有解析解\[
u(x,y) = \sin(\pi x)\cosh(\pi y)
\]其中 \(x \[0,1], y\[0,1]\)
